    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>建设火星，统领星辰！</strong></h2>随着地球资源的枯竭，人类已经迁移到遥远的火星。现在，您的机会来了！在Build Master: MarsVille中，您被邀请开创这颗迷人红色星球上最发达的殖民地。随着殖民地规模和管理复杂性的增长，您做出的每个决策都将塑造其命运！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366120/extras/5053bbb166a5284704b6442928165f8a.poster.avif?t=1702347589\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366120/extras/5053bbb166a5284704b6442928165f8a.webm?t=1702347589\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366120/extras/5053bbb166a5284704b6442928165f8a.mp4?t=1702347589\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>为您的殖民地注入生机</strong></h2>从未被涉足的火星原野出发，打造您梦寐以求的城市。兴建摩天大楼、公园、桥梁和各式建筑，合理地规划城市结构，提高资源生产效率，满足市民的各种需求，确保您的殖民地可以持续的发展。在这个严酷星球上，您的每个抉择都关乎存亡。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366120/extras/c9740c6352c57472c2aade4b9169c6b8.poster.avif?t=1702347589\" width=632 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366120/extras/c9740c6352c57472c2aade4b9169c6b8.webm?t=1702347589\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366120/extras/c9740c6352c57472c2aade4b9169c6b8.mp4?t=1702347589\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>在火星上蓬勃发展</strong></h2>从未开垦的火星的大地上采集各种资源，用战略性眼光布局建筑。与其他成员交换补给，促进您殖民地的繁荣。做出重要的财务决策，平衡对城市、军事和英雄的投资，以确保市民满意度和发展进度。英雄们各自拥有独特的技能，对于保障城市管理的顺畅运作至关重要。同时，您的城市可能会面临外星海盗和沙虫的威胁。当战斗来临时，指挥您的英雄们来抵御这些入侵者！<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366120/extras/6bf57cebf2f699656463d11f39168f4c.poster.avif?t=1702347589\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366120/extras/6bf57cebf2f699656463d11f39168f4c.webm?t=1702347589\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366120/extras/6bf57cebf2f699656463d11f39168f4c.mp4?t=1702347589\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>发挥您的工程才智</strong></h2>在火星建设过程中，您将面临众多富有挑战性的工程难题。释放您的创造力和工程技能，展现您的桥梁建造本领。每个关卡都会呈现令人叹为观止的风景和崭新的挑战。您精心打造的桥梁是否足以经受住重压呢？紧绷神经，亲历激动人心的瞬间！当然，失败也在所难免。桥梁崩塌或卡车坠落的时刻将为您提供宝贵的教训，驱使您不断精进技艺。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366120/extras/6479902149e8520ae7b37f22266441e1.poster.avif?t=1702347589\" width=650 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366120/extras/6479902149e8520ae7b37f22266441e1.webm?t=1702347589\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366120/extras/6479902149e8520ae7b37f22266441e1.mp4?t=1702347589\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>团队协作，夺取胜利</strong></h2>与其他殖民者建立紧密联系，联手对抗外部威胁。共享资源，讨论战略，促进共同繁荣。挑战竞争对手的殖民地，争夺宝贵资源，沉浸在星际战争的激情中。在排行榜上崭露头角，积累声誉和奖励。在关键时刻，您的战略智慧将直接决定胜负的走向。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366120/extras/0a48ff6434e9a34ca086f48c94dbc164.poster.avif?t=1702347589\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366120/extras/0a48ff6434e9a34ca086f48c94dbc164.webm?t=1702347589\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366120/extras/0a48ff6434e9a34ca086f48c94dbc164.mp4?t=1702347589\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
